In this game you can fly around  and eat tacos to earn taco$ and buy powers and skins, to become the ultimate taco eater! This is the 4th and only game made on unity and the other games were made on scratch. This game uses 2d sprites in a 3d world (because i cant find a 3d model) this game controls using WASD and UP and DOWN ARROWS to fly up and down and all around!
